  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All ACLF due to HEV

          -  Consent to participate in trial and collection of blood.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant and nursing mothers.

          -  Severe anemia

          -  Other etiologies of ACLF (eg. Alcohol, drugs, reactivation of hepatitis B and
             hepatitis C, variceal bleeding, surgical intervention and sepsis)

          -  Hepatocellular carcinoma (HCC)

          -  Hepatorenal syndrome (HRS) at admission

          -  Presence of life threatening cardiovascular, respiratory and neurological disease

          -  Acquired Immunodeficiency Syndrome

          -  Patients with hemoglobinopathies (e.g., thalassemia major, sickle-cell anemia)

          -  Refusal to provide consent to participate in the study
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
